data.desc:
- Developed new features and maintained some of NOBI APIs using Laravel and Nodejs.
- Migrated a portion of NOBI's monolithic API to a microservices architecture.
- Transferred specific NOBI APIs from Laravel to Golang.
- Developed new features and maintained internal applications for NOBI utilizing Laravel and Vue.js.

- Developed new features and maintained Titik Pintar API, integral to our mobile application, internal systems, and other applications using Laravel.
- Developed new features and maintained Titik Pintar Admin Panel for our internal team using Angular.js.
- Developed new features and maintained Sahabat Pintar application using Laravel and Angular.js. This platform caters to teachers, designers, and animators, facilitating their contributions to our learning application.
- Developed new features and maintained Titik Pintar Account Login using Laravel and React.js. This app is a user-friendly website empowering parents to monitor their children's progress within our application.
- Innovated various features such as multiplayer, live class functionality, automation, and more, benefiting both end-users and the internal team using Node.js.

- Developed new features and maintained web applications for clients of PT Wamplo Satu Interteknologi using Laravel.
- Developed new features and maintained mobile applications for clients of PT Wamplo Satu Interteknologi using React Native.

- Conducted thorough testing of applications for ICON+ clients.
- Contributed to the development of applications tailored to ICON+ clients, utilizing Angular.js.
